{"tid":2333936,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"12港人送中︱專訪︱黃偉然母親：只有兒子平安回家 才是真正冬至！","createTime":"2020-12-20T21:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T06:47:12.000Z","uid":130626,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"411eca4d083dececfe157b1d0cb3284f694283fd","tid":2333936,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T21:20:34.000Z","msg":"冬至慶團圓，12個家庭卻因為家人被秘密扣押大陸，無法團聚，深圳市鹽田區人民檢察院上周公佈正式起訴涉潛逃台灣的12名港人中的10人，包括30歲的黃偉然。黃太及黃母在偉然受審前夕接受《蘋果》專訪，細數逾百日失去親人的思念，偉然消失前穿過的衣服，黃太一直不肯洗，只為把丈夫的氣味留在家。失去偉然的黃家未能團聚做冬，黃母說兒子平安回港前不會慶祝任何節日：「只有佢平安回家，先係我哋一家真正嘅冬至」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201221/JJUEEDY4RNEKDFS2G7D72FGAFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201221%2FJJUEEDY4RNEKDFS2G7D72FGAFM%2F&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIco9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=70672246\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201221%2FJJUEEDY4RNEKDFS2G7D72FGAFM%2F&h=7313e4d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201221/JJUEEDY4RNEKDFS2G7D72FGAFM/</a>"},{"pid":"a7004651c003a88587738b4742922dcf343a9b73","tid":2333936,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T21:20:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09c32fbed3613588c718630f59c16980b05e9732","tid":2333936,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T21:21:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a2aba3f599a0c672d8efa57f420421517c22d5f","tid":2333936,"uid":167509,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T21:30:26.000Z","msg":"堅持！<br />\n好快出返黎，到時再壯大黃圈"},{"pid":"1293e68682eee7ea48abbd839bedfaa2b1ec667d","tid":2333936,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T22:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c635b21dbc4737fe052e84e1d14ff958e8cca0a","tid":2333936,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0